title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show NOV-06-2013 WED
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show NOV-06-2013 WED









The Glenn Beck Program

          Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm 



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 11/6/13Wednesday, November 06, 2013 11:54 AM





Glenn goes over the recent election results and the bad news it brings

 as Bill Deblasio, a self pro-claimed socialist wins the NYC mayoral run 

  and Chris Christie is re-elected as Governor of NJ.


  Also, David Barton joins the program to announce his run for the Senate.

  Plus the unbelievable story out of New Mexico about a man who received a body cavity search
     for running a stop sign.
